title: Norfolk State prepares for preseason favorite North Carolina A
text:
Norfolk State prepares for preseason favorite North Carolina A&T The Spartans are 2-0 in the MEAC. The Aggies were the preseason pick to win the conference. The Aggies were the preseason pick to win the conference.  //on.wvec.com/1RwKPbb   Norfolk State prepares for preseason favorite North Carolina A&T The Spartans are 2-0 in MEAC. The Aggies were the preseason pick to win the conference. Scott Cash , 13News Now 6:53 p.m. EDT October 8, 2015 CONNECT   
Three games against FBS schools to start the schedule seems to have toughened up Norfolk State. The Spartans lost those three games, but have rebounded nicely to win their first two games in the MEAC. 
Conference preseason favorite, North Carolina A&T comes to Dick Price Stadium this Saturday at 2 pm. 
NSU had a dramatic come from behind win over Howard last week. They point to the win over Hampton the week before, as a kick start to the season.  //on.wvec.com/1RwKPbb TOP VIDEOS
